{"tid":938890,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"領展出售12商場近4800車位 作價120億","createTime":"2018-12-12T16:14:43.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-13T01:30:39.000Z","uid":28765,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"591698fbf33cdd26309635d5e90c9eff788a717f","tid":938890,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T16:14:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181212/large/1544618873_d05a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181212%2Flarge%2F1544618873_d05a.jpg&h=4d9d6a88&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181212/large/1544623681_eda7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181212%2Flarge%2F1544623681_eda7.jpg&h=52e110b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n售價最高及規模最大為屯門山景邨商場，連638個車位，9月份估值約14.5億元水平，最後售價為18.36億元。<br />\n<br />\n領展(823)公佈，成功於12月12日出售12項物業，並與基滙資本為首的財團簽訂買賣協議，總代價為120.1億元。<br />\n<br />\n12項物業包括鴨脷洲、秦石、景林、利東、明德等物場，物業較9月30日的估值高約32.1%，物業出售的淨收益為27.876億元。<br />\n涉及12商場包括屯門山景商場、粉嶺華明商場、鴨脷洲利東商場、鴨脷洲邨之商舖及停車場、沙田秦石商場、寶琳景林商場、將軍澳明德商場、粉嶺華心商場、橫頭磡村宏暉中心、屯門兆禧苑商場、長沙灣幸福商場、上水太平邨之商舖及停車場。總內部樓面面積達57.8625萬方呎，涉及車位達4789個，本年9月30日物業估值達90.9億元。<br />\n<br />\n售價最高及規模最大為屯門山景邨商場，面積約12.143萬方呎，連638個車位，9月份估值約14.5億元水平，最後售價為18.36億元，較9月底估值高出26%。另外，鄰近港鐵站的有鴨脷洲利東商場、秦石邨商場、橫頭磡邨宏暉中心等，分別靠近利東站、車公廟站及樂富站，總面積約17.25萬方呎，涉1560個車位。<br />\n領展行政總裁王國龍表示，儘管近期市況波動，是次物業銷售獲得頂級國際投資者，包括全球和區域性私募基金，以及本地投資者的熱烈反應。競爭性投標和最終銷售價格比對上一次出售物業的作價更為吸引，突顯了全球投資者對香港經濟及房地產業的信心。<br />\n出售物業後，計入於今年11月26日購入北京京通羅斯福廣場，領展將有約90.1%資產位於香港，約9.9%位於中國內地。投資組合總值將約2,040億元。<br />\n出售資產所得收益，將用於香港及中國內地一線城市的新投資機會，以及債務償還、基金單位回購等一般營運資金用途。物業出售將於2019年3月13日落實成交。<br />\n領展月初股價曾創79.55元上市新高，今日收報77.9元，升近1%。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20181212/59023260\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181212%2F59023260&d=WiINB%2FuBF7B3OimJZRA9sC7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=e0f6ad0c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181212%2F59023260&h=bd82e6c0\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20181212/59023260</a>"},{"pid":"d21489ee2d4e8e5f163668060d29f4e3066f9469","tid":938890,"uid":24730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T16:32:50.000Z","msg":"世澤講兩句"},{"pid":"f89a7156d15335a7caf4046f09f79cfbbd789525","tid":938890,"uid":155773,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T16:36:28.000Z","msg":"轉個頭咪又係去買大陸房地產"},{"pid":"5970b50fa7694506e014c854bc934fc0b195bd26","tid":938890,"uid":216780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T16:40:11.000Z","msg":"留名聽日823仆街"},{"pid":"2834c3827a3ecf7df35e86ce86b5894b88ec6869","tid":938890,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T16:52:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20309e6cd79b46871851f647bcf2c109cdbba2ee","tid":938890,"uid":128603,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T17:45:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://sparkpost.files.wordpress.com/2011/10/2604769434481454942.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsparkpost.files.wordpress.com%2F2011%2F10%2F2604769434481454942.jpg&h=475a2b15&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"eba727369e0359e4ca7659d86073f0f4f24d0938","tid":938890,"uid":75232,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"20309e6cd79b46871851f647bcf2c109cdbba2ee","tid":938890,"uid":128603,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T17:45:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://sparkpost.files.wordpress.com/2011/10/2604769434481454942.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsparkpost.files.wordpress.com%2F2011%2F10%2F2604769434481454942.jpg&h=